Linc Edochie, brother to the Nollywood actor, Yul Edochie, has stated that he is not in support of her brother’s second marriage to the Nigerian actress, Judy Austin. Recall that the actor on Wednesday via his Instagram page announced the existence of his son and his marriage to the mother of the child, declaring her publicly as his second wife. However, his brother while responding to a follower on his Instagram page in regards to Yul’s second marriage, stated that he wasn’t present at the traditional marriage. The follower, @angy_talks01 wrote, “ You see wetin your brother do. You follow them go pay bride price on Sunday abi you no follow? Answer me now. Linc responded by saying, “Please don’t piss me off. I wasn’t there.”